      "css": ".cv{position:relative;height:100%;background:#100d0b;color:#f3efe8;font-family:'Pretendard','Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden}.cv__media,.cv__veil,.cv__grain{position:absolute;inset:0}.cv__media{background:#140f0d}.cv__media img{width:100%;height:100%;display:block;object-fit:cover;object-position:50% 18%;transform:scale(1.18);filter:contrast(.92) brightness(.82) saturate(.78) sepia(.18) blur(1.05px)}.cv__veil{background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 29%,rgba(255,225,196,.24),rgba(255,225,196,0) 17%),radial-gradient(circle at 50% 68%,rgba(235,199,170,.16),rgba(235,199,170,0) 18%),linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(14,10,9,.12),rgba(14,10,9,.04) 16%,rgba(14,10,9,.16) 34%,rgba(14,10,9,.38) 60%,rgba(14,10,9,.74) 100%),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(12,9,8,.24),rgba(12,9,8,0) 17%,rgba(12,9,8,0) 82%,rgba(12,9,8,.28) 100%)}.cv__grain{background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.18) .65px,transparent .95px),radial-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.22) .9px,transparent 1.15px),repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.022) 0 1px,transparent 1px 3px),linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.04),rgba(255,255,255,0));background-size:2px 2px,4px 4px,3px 100%,100% 100%;mix-blend-mode:soft-light;opacity:.78;pointer-events:none}.cv__tag{position:absolute;top:126px;font-family:'neue-haas-grotesk-display','Helvetica Neue','Arial',sans-serif;font-size:35px;line-height:1;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:0;color:rgba(243,239,232,.9)}.cv__tag--left{left:68px}.cv__tag--right{right:68px}.cv__content{position:absolute;left:68px;top:1018px;right:68px}.cv__title{margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:26px;max-width:860px;font-family:'Pretendard','Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;font-size:86px;line-height:1;font-weight:800;word-break:keep-all;color:#f2eee7;text-shadow:0 3px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16)}.cv__title span{display:block;letter-spacing:.02em}"
    },
    {
      "theme": "light",
      "chrome": "none",
      "footer": "none",
      "html": "<section class='ed' style='--ed-image-position:50% 42%;--ed-image-scale:1.04'><div class='ed__media'><img src='https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/medium-shot-man-working-late-night-laptop_23-2150280996.jpg' alt='man lit by a laptop late at night' /></div><div class='ed__grain'></div><div class='ed__content'><div class='ed__meta'><span class='ed__index'>[01]</span><span class='ed__rule'></span></div><h2 class='ed__title'>우리는 왜 과로를<br />성공의 증거처럼 믿을까</h2><p class='ed__body'>우리는 성과를 오래 관찰하기보다, 성공한 사람의 혹독한 순간을 더 선명하게 기억한다. 그래서 결과를 만든 구조는 놓치고, 밤늦게까지 버티는 태도만 성공의 공식처럼 받아들인다. 문제는 그 복제가 성과보다 소모를 먼저 가져온다는 점이다.</p><p class='ed__note'>성과보다 서사가 더 강하게 유통될 때, 과로는 곧 성공처럼 보이기 시작한다.</p></div></section>",
      "css": ".ed{--ed-bg:#e6e0d8;--ed-text:#131210;--ed-body:#433e38;--ed-edge:92px;--ed-top:76px;--ed-bottom:100px;--ed-media-height:470px;--ed-image-position:50% 36%;--ed-image-scale:1.04;position:relative;height:100%;background:var(--ed-bg);color:var(--ed-text);padding:var(--ed-top) var(--ed-edge) var(--ed-bottom);font-family:'Pretendard','Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;display:grid;grid-template-rows:var(--ed-media-height) 1fr;gap:30px;overflow:hidden}.ed__media{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;background:#d0c9c0}.ed__media::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(6,6,6,.04),rgba(6,6,6,.16));pointer-events:none}.ed__media img{width:100%;height:100%;display:block;object-fit:cover;object-position:var(--ed-image-position);transform:scale(var(--ed-image-scale));transform-origin:center;filter:grayscale(.28) saturate(.82) contrast(1.02) brightness(.92) sepia(.02)}.ed__grain{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.13) .7px,transparent .9px),radial-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.16) .8px,transparent 1px),repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.018) 0 1px,transparent 1px 3px),linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.04),rgba(255,255,255,0));background-size:4px 4px,6px 6px,3px 100%,100% 100%;mix-blend-mode:soft-light;opacity:.42;pointer-events:none}.ed__content{position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:0}.ed__meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px}.ed__index{font-size:28px;line-height:1;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.035em;color:rgba(20,19,17,.96)}.ed__rule{height:2px;flex:1;background:rgba(20,19,17,.84);transform:translateY(1px)}.ed__title{margin:24px 0 0;max-width:850px;font-size:56px;line-height:1.09;letter-spacing:-.056em;font-weight:700;word-break:keep-all;text-wrap:balance}.ed__body{margin:22px 0 0;max-width:860px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.8;letter-spacing:-.018em;color:var(--ed-body);font-weight:500;word-break:keep-all}.ed__note{margin-top:auto;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(20,19,17,.16);max-width:820px;font-size:18px;line-height:1.72;letter-spacing:-.012em;color:#5d5751;font-weight:500;word-break:keep-all}"
    },
    {
      "theme": "light",
      "chrome": "none",
      "footer": "none",
      "html": "<section class='ed' style='--ed-image-position:50% 44%;--ed-image-scale:1.03'><div class='ed__media'><img src='https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/workplace-office-with-laptop-coffee-dark-room-night_169016-47422.jpg' alt='dark laptop desk with coffee under a single light' /></div><div class='ed__grain'></div><div class='ed__content'><div class='ed__meta'><span class='ed__index'>[02]</span><span class='ed__rule'></span></div><h2 class='ed__title'>Bill Roche의 반전은<br />일을 줄인 뒤 시작됐다</h2><p class='ed__body'>그는 더 많은 일을 하는 사람이 아니라, 덜 중요한 일을 덜어낸 뒤 오히려 사업의 결과와 판단의 선명도가 좋아졌다고 말한다. 이 반전은 성과가 시간 총량의 함수가 아니라는 사실을 보여준다. 더 오래 버티는 것보다 무엇을 남기고 무엇을 버릴지가 먼저라는 뜻이다.</p><p class='ed__note'>많이 하는 것과 잘되는 것은 같은 말이 아니다.</p></div></section>",
